*″Culture, Civilization and German Anti-Semitism″ in &quot;Judaism&quot; Vol. 7 #2 Summer 1958
*″Mystical Origins of National Socialism″ in &quot;Journal of the History of Ideas&quot; Vol. XXII #1 Jan.–May 1961

