*Clinton Grove in Weare, NH and Clinton Grove Academy, also in Weare, NH.
*The Dewitt Clinton - Apartment building in Astoria, Queens, NYC built c. 1928

==See also==
* &quot;DeWitt Clinton&quot; was also the name of the first steam locomotive to operate in New York; it ran between Albany and Schenectady, New York.

